This if for OEM, if you need a cd-key you should look somewhere else. OEM means it came pre-installed on the machine, and you just enter the cd-key on the machine.

If you want a cd-key look somewhere else, this is only the boot disk. And legal as far as it goes. 

You should download this if you need only the boot-disk. 

Cheers!
